Teen from Lahore in Punjab province is recovering from burns to 55 percent of his body after he was beaten and burnt with Kerosene . 
  He was approached by two Muslim youths as he left Friday prayers in Lahore . 
  The two boys asked him about his religion and when he said he was Christian they beat him and set him on fire . 
  He is recovering in hospital from burns and is identified only as Nuaman . 
 